dct_title_s: Map of the country twenty miles round Wells : taken from Bacon’s county map of Somersetshire, for F. George’s, Swan Hotel, visitors’ guide
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Advertisements on verso. Includes illustration of Wells Cathedral. Probably issued in: The Swan Hotel visitors' guide to Wells. Rev. ed. Bath : W. Lewis, 1880.
dct_publisher_sm: Bath : W. Lewis Lith. Herald Office, [1880]
